<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4890154>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 38. External view of left valves of Macroscapha inaequata Maddocks, 1990, Macroscapha scotia sp. nov.; and Macroscapha walterae sp. nov. Macroscapha inaequata Maddocks, 1990: A, adult female (SNB 0752, ZMH K-40821); B, adult male (SNB 0578-DNA 285. ZMH K-41487); H, (SNB 0052); I, (SNB 0053); J, adult female (SNB 0054) (ZMH 40819). Macroscapha scotia sp. nov.: C, paratype A (ZMH K-35501); D, holotype adult male (SNB 0739, ZMH K-40820); E, paratype adult male (SNB 0022); F, paratype adult female (SNB 0056); G, paratype adult female (SNB 0741) (ZMH K-40837). Macroscapha walterae sp. nov.: K, holotype adult male (SNB 0745, ZMH K-41484); L, paratype adult male (SNB 0051); M, paratype adult male (SNB 0750); N, paratype adult female (SNB 0048) (ZMH K-40818). Scale bar = 500 Mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4890154/files/figure.png" .

