        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 40. Appendages V and hemipenis of Macroscapha inaequata Maddocks, 1990 and Macroscapha walterae sp. nov. Macroscapha inaequata Maddocks, 1990: A, adult male (SNB 0021, ZMH K-40819); B, adult male (SNB 0052, ZMH K-40819); C, adult male (SNB 0099-DNA 2, ZMH K-41487); D, adult male (SNB 576-DNA 283, ZMH K-40822); E, adult male (SNB 0753, ZMH K-40822); F, adult male (SNB 0053, ZMH K-40819); G, adult male (SNB 0579-DNA 286, ZMH K-41487). Macroscapha walterae sp. nov.: H, O, P, paratype adult male (SNB 0745, ZMH K-41484); I, paratype adult male (SNB 0746, ZMH K-41485); J, paratype adult male (SNB 0422-DNA 129, ZMH K-41485); K, N, paratype adult male (SNB 0119-DNA 22, ZMH K-41480); L, paratype adult male (SNB 0051, ZMH K-40818); M, paratype adult male (SNB 0750, ZMH K-40818). A–E, H–M, hemipenis; F, G, O, P, male appendage V; N, copulatory rod of hemipenis. Scale bars = 100 Mm." ;
