<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4890156>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 39. Appendages V, VI, and VII and furcae of Macroscapha inaequata Maddocks, 1990, Macroscapha rehmi sp. nov., Macroscapha scotia sp. nov., Macroscapha turbida (Müller, 1908), and Macroscapha walterae sp. nov. Macroscapha scotia sp. nov.: A, paratype adult female (SNB 0024); L, M, paratype adult male (SNB 0738), ZMH K-40837. Macroscapha rehmi sp. nov.: B, paratype adult female (SNB 0028); N, O, paratype adult male (SNB 0743); ZMH K-40836. Macroscapha turbida (Müller, 1908): C, adult female (SNB 0348-DNA 85); I, adult male (SNB 0355); R, adult male (SNB 0351-DNA 88); S, adult male (SNB 0347-DNA 84) (ZMH K-41476); T, U, paralectotype (SNB 0747, ZMB 13133). Macroscapha inaequata Maddocks, 1990: D, adult female (SNB 0752, ZMH K-40821); H, adult male (SNB 0753, ZMH K-40822). Macroscapha walterae sp. nov.: E, paratype adult female (SNB 0611-DNA 318); F, J, K, paratype adult female (SNB 0462-DNA 169); G, P, (A-1) male paratype (SNB 0612-DNA 319); Q, paratype (A-1) male (SNB 0613-DNA 320) (ZMH K-41485). A–E, female appendage V; F, appendage VI; G–I, K, furca; J, appendage VII; L–O, R–U, male appendage V; P, Q, (A-1) appendage V. Scale bars = 100 Mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4890156/files/figure.png" .
